snippet.title: Cosmic Boll - Pre Sage2020 demo test
snippet.description:
I have been gifted a laptop recently to replace the slow one with the death-clicking HD so I'm using it to record a progress vídeo for Cosmic Boll, gameplay mishaps and all. Not like I can complain given the kind circunstances of the gift, but laptops where the up and down Keys are half-sized are a pain for playing games...

Still two-something months before Sage 2020. Hope I can pull it off this time, lol.
Stages: 5/6
Bosses: 1/6

https://yoritoshi.itch.io/cosmic-boll
